</paragraph>
</caption>
<paragraph id="8B91BC26FFA0633F73230433FDDF4155" blockId="55.[264,1323,283,430]" pageId="55" pageNumber="56">
<emphasis id="B95A6034FFA0633F73230433FD4D413E" bold="true" box="[312,680,283,309]" pageId="55" pageNumber="56">Derivation of specific epithet.</emphasis>
