<emphasis id="B95A6034FFA0633F70EE0434FCB6413E" box="[757,851,284,309]" italics="true" pageId="55" pageNumber="56">hirsutus</emphasis>
for hairy, referring to the dense setae at the apex of the ovipositor.
</paragraph>
